  /* ── Card response — applies at EVERY breakpoint ─────────────────
     Lifted out of the mobile @media block so the desktop header
     search (#yuval-header-search) drives the same gravitational
     filter response on the orbit as the mobile Core Search panel.
     Uses the standalone `scale` + `filter` + `opacity` properties so
     the existing `transform` on `.galaxy-card` (orbit positioning
